{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/go-memory/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"F&Y-BLOG","author":"kimifdw"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"4efb7048-a671-52dd-8488-d9f026c80fd2","html":"<h1 id=\"策略\"><a href=\"#%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>策略</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>MADV_FREE</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>内核会在进程的页表中将这些页标记为“未分配”，从而进程的 RSS 就会变小。OS 后续可以将对应的物理页分配给其他进程。</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>MADV_DONTNEED</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>内核只会在页表中将这些进程页面标记为可回收，在需要的时候才回收这些页面</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"应用版本\"><a href=\"#%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>应用版本</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>Go1.12之前，使用<strong>MADV_DONTNEED</strong>策略</li>\n<li>Go1.12-1.15，使用<strong>MADV_FREE</strong>策略【linux内核版本>=4.5】</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"madv_free带来的问题\"><a href=\"#madv_free%E5%B8%A6%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>MADV_FREE带来的问题</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>引发用户体验的问题</li>\n<li>混淆统计信息和监控工具的情况</li>\n<li>导致与内存使用有关联的个别管理系统集成不良</li>\n<li>挤压同主机上的其他应用资源</li>\n</ol>","timeToRead":1,"frontmatter":{"title":"golang内存管理","date":"February 18, 2021","spoiler":"go 内存管理"},"fields":{"slug":"/go-memory/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/go-memory/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/OLAP/","directoryName":"OLAP"},"frontmatter":{"title":"OLAP笔记"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/cms/","directoryName":"cms"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Concurrent Mark Sweep(CMS)回收器"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["336482444"]}